
Let's make English pronunciation checker feature

View - PronunciationCheckerView
Controller - PronunciationCheckerController

TtsService - wrapper for flutter_tts package manages text to speech
SpeechRecognitionService - wrapper for speech_to_text package manages speech regognition

View: 
textfield for entering text 
play button to play text using text to speech

microphone button to record user voice

SpeechRecognitionService convert record to text
PronunciationCheckerController compares recognized text to the text from textfield and displays feedback like "Good", "Excelent" or "Try again", "You can do better"

